Package gw.api.webservice.messagingTools

Class Summary
Acknowledgement Acknowledgement contains information to be returned to ClaimCenter about processing of a message by an external system.
CustomEvents Custom events to fire on an object as part of an acknowledgement.
FieldChanges Stores a list of field changes for an object that is applied as part of an acknowledgement The field changes are stored in an array of RemoteFieldValue, which is essentially a name/value pair.
FieldChangeValue RemoteFieldValue is essentially a name value pair.
FieldValue FieldValue is essentially a name value pair.
MessageOptionalFields Deprecated. replaced by plugin-based messaging.
